Package: GLMMadaptive
Title: Generalized Linear Mixed Models using Adaptive Gaussian Quadrature
Version: 0.1-0
Author: Dimitris Rizopoulos <d.rizopoulos@erasmusmc.nl>
Maintainer: Dimitris Rizopoulos <d.rizopoulos@erasmusmc.nl>
Description: Fits generalized linear mixed models for a single grouping factor under
    maximum likelihood approximating the intergrals over the random effects with an 
    adaptive Gaussian quadrature rule.
Imports: MASS, nlme, parallel
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/drizopoulos/GLMMadaptive
